{"tid":1681153,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉載］每日清算CCTVB 今日任務：森下仁丹","createTime":"2019-10-29T08:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T08:50:18.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a36ddce9efa4c5fe6c1097de092c67df576d783","tid":1681153,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:42:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>轟炸電郵任務，#2 有詳細點人數</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第4️⃣批電郵：147 --&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>158人</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(請補做：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PkEVlb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PkEVlb&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=0d4f6ba7\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2PkEVlb</a>)<br />\n<blockquote>如果email打晒回頭、或者Gmail唔俾send<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. 轉email title<br />\n2. 轉用Yahoo / Hotmail<br />\n3. 電郵title隔空格，請自行創作：強 烈 要 求 不 與 無 綫 電 視 簽 訂 廣 告 合 約<br />\n4. 電郵內容隔空格<br />\nTemplate - <a href=\"https://lih.kg/mJvbgkX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/mJvbgkX</a></span></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">事實證明，洗版真係work，<br />\n如果咁都唔參與，問心你究竟幾想TVB執笠？</span></strong></span><br />\n鈣思健回應尋日洗版行動，但未有表明不會commit 2020廣告費<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/73269694_484657259057795_5792017510396067840_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_eui2=AeG3uzMwahq3eZD2nSKU0-ZDcwJZ_IOayghJg2rTmLMKk8KPH0xaT7HP8XEX6FrVQg_AmhM2tsAcCgYZtt_5xO1BSpGHEQwDrLQuXVk9WVJp3w&amp;_nc_oc=AQn31e3YfF4tu7zbFz2GdqzZsyHS9QlIWuIAH4R-ecmUWzRhlML8hqPmHDbSgNt6vek&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=bd70f9b3ecd69ea0f779a3b3bb9c574b&amp;oe=5E23657A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F73269694_484657259057795_5792017510396067840_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_eui2%3DAeG3uzMwahq3eZD2nSKU0-ZDcwJZ_IOayghJg2rTmLMKk8KPH0xaT7HP8XEX6FrVQg_AmhM2tsAcCgYZtt_5xO1BSpGHEQwDrLQuXVk9WVJp3w%26_nc_oc%3DAQn31e3YfF4tu7zbFz2GdqzZsyHS9QlIWuIAH4R-ecmUWzRhlML8hqPmHDbSgNt6vek%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3Dbd70f9b3ecd69ea0f779a3b3bb9c574b%26oe%3D5E23657A&h=7f0a7b3d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <br />\n【抵制CCTVB 每日任務】<br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <br />\n <br />\n是日精選@29 Oct 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>森下仁丹</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jintan.HK.official/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjintan.HK.official%2F&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=dd1405cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jintan.HK.official/</a></span></strong><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>※新留言template，全力阻止廣告商簽訂下年合約</strong> <br />\n</span></span>無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42PkT8u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42PkT8u.jpg&h=0ec9b76f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<strong>講下臭屎</strong><br />\n呃錢呃得咁開心？落TVB廣告，唯有踢爆你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1️⃣ 【膠原蛋白飲品】入到胃，拆散哂變胺基酸。你估識原條去塊面咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食雞蛋仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2️⃣ 【美肌丸】醫學建議，維他命C每日65-90毫克 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為咗賺錢，叫人食1000毫克！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3️⃣ 【輔酶Q10 】研究顯示，口服得0.04%溶到係血 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要效果無FDA認可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n黑心度：5/5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\nSource:<br />\n膠原蛋白迷思 - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Wh6ywW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Wh6ywW&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=1e5412d0\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Wh6ywW</a><br />\nVC建議量 - <a href=\"http://mayocl.in/2oly7sn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmayocl.in%2F2oly7sn&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=a27aa5ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://mayocl.in/2oly7sn</a><br />\n輔酶Q10生物利用度 - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2qHtkSS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qHtkSS&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=a5a4342d\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2qHtkSS</a><br />\n <br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得bookmark</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</strong></span> <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=aa0340af\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a>  <br />\n －－－－－－－ <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請即follow:</span></strong> <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/l